<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your Stellar Disbursement Platform account password. Please use the confirmation token <strong>{{.ResetToken}}</strong> on the <a href="{{.ResetPasswordLink}}">reset password page</a> to create a new password.</p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this message or reach out to your organization's administrator with any questions or concerns.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The {{.OrganizationName}} Team</p>
</body>
</html>
